title: 126: Who's for real in the NFL, who can turn things around?
itunes:title: 126: Who's for real in the NFL, who can turn things around?
description:
Previewing Week 6 of the NFL season, former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down which one-loss team may struggle down the stretch, and what middle of the pack teams can make a playoff run. The duo also talks college football with a special guest.
